Package: tidydrc
Type: Package
Title: Tidy modelling of dose-response relationships with the drc package
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Angel",  "Angelov", email = "aangeloo@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
